;  vertical-align:middle;&#34&gt;\r\n                &lt;/a&gt;\r\n            &lt;/h1&gt;\r\n            &lt;h2 style=&#34text-align: right; padding:0; margin:0; margin-left:auto; line-height:1.333; color:#252525; font-size:24px; font-weight:400;&#34&gt;\r\n                아이디찾기 안내메일\r\n            &lt;/h2&gt;\r\n    &lt;/div&gt;\r\n        &lt;section class=&#34mailing_container&#34 style=&#34padding: 6% 5% 9%; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&#34&gt;\r\n            &lt;h3 style=&#34margin: 15px 0px; padding: 0;&#34&gt;\r\n                &lt;font color=&#34#2985db&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 26px;&#34&gt;한국도선안전교육센터&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 26px;&#34&gt;에 가입하신 것을 환영합니다!&lt;/span&gt;\r\n            &lt;/h3&gt;\r\n            &lt;p style=&#34line-height: 24px; font-size: 14px;&#34&gt;\r\n                고객님의 아이디는 [member_id] 입니다.\r\n            &lt;/p&gt;\r\n            &lt;p style=&#34line-height: 24px; font-size: 14px;&#34&gt;\r\n                앞으로도 고객님을 위해 최선을 다하는 한국도선안전교육센터 가(이) 되도록 노력하겠습니다.\r\n            &lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;/section&gt;\r\n        &lt;section class=&#34mailing_container2&#34 style=&#34margin: 30px 0px 0px; padding: 5%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&#34&gt;\r\n            &lt;p style=&#34line-height: 1.333; letter-spacing: -1px; font-size: 13px;&#34&gt;\r\n                본 메일은 발신전용 메일이며 문의에 대한 회신 처리되지 않습니다. 문의사항은 고객센터를 이용해주세요.&lt;br&gt;\r\n                회원이 아니신 경우나 메일 수신거부 회원이신데도 메일을 받으신다면&lt;a href=&#34mailto:kopec@kmpilot.or.kr&#34 style=&#34color: #252525; letter-spacing: -0.5px; font-size: 12px; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); text-decoration-line: none;&#34 target=&#34_blank&#34&gt; kopec@kmpilot.or.kr &lt;/a&gt;으로 연락해 주세요.\r\n            &lt;/p&gt;\r\n        &lt;/section&gt;\r\n        &lt;div id=&#34footer&#34 class=&#34mailing_footer&#34 style=&#34margin-top:40px;&#34&gt;\r\n            &lt;div class=&#34footer_bot&#34 style=&#34height:120px; background-color:#f2f2f2;&#34&gt;\r\n                &lt;div class=&#34wrap_layout&#34 style=&#34padding: 0 20px; width:100%;  box-sizing:border-box;&#34&gt;\r\n                    &lt;div class=&#34f_content&#34&gt;\r\n                        &lt;address style=&#34 font-family:&#39돋움&#39,&#39dotum&#39; font-size:12px; color:#959595; font-weight:300; font-style:normal; line-height:22px; letter-spacing:-0.5px; display:block;&#34&gt;\r\n                            한국도선안전교육센터  &lt;span class=&#34bar&#34&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;  서울 서초구 반포대로 94 (서초동) 5층  &lt;span class=&#34bar&#34&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;  대표 윤호섭, 여명준     \r\n                        &lt;/address&gt;\r\n                        &lt;p style=&#34 font-family:&#39돋움&#39,&#39dotum&#39; font-size:12px; color:#959595; font-weight:300; font-style:normal; line-height:22px; letter-spacing:-0.5px; margin:0;padding:0;&#34&gt;\r\n                            사업자등록번호 받아야함  &lt;span class=&#34bar&#34&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;  통신판매업신고  &lt;/p&gt;\r\n                        &lt;p style=&#34 font-family:&#39돋움&#39,&#39dotum&#39; font-size:12px; color:#959595; font-weight:300; font-style:normal; line-height:22px; letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin:0;padding:0;&#34&gt;\r\n                            고객센터 &lt;a href=&#34tel:02-780-8042&#34 style=&#34 text-decoration:none; color:#959595&#34&gt;02-780-80422&lt;/a&gt;   &lt;span class=&#34bar&#34&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;  이메일 :&lt;a href=&#34mailto:kopec@kmpilot.or.kr&#34 style=&#34text-decoration:none; color:#252525;&#34&gt; kopec@kmpilot.or.kr&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n                        &lt;br&gt;\r\n                        &lt;p class=&#34copy&#34 style=&#34 font-family:&#39돋움&#39,&#39dotum&#39; font-size:12px; color:#959595; font-weight:300; font-style:normal; line-height:22px; letter-spacing:-0.5px;margin:0;padding:0;&#34&gt;\r\n                            Copyright © &lt;a href=&#34https://kopec1.cafe24.com/&#34 style=&#34text-decoration:none; color:#959595&#34&gt; 한국도선안전교육센터 &lt;/a&gt