: border-box;&#34&gt;전부승소&lt;/span&gt;판결&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;을 이끌어냈습니다&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&#34en-us&#34 xml:lang=&#34en-us&#34 style=&#34box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13pt;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 나눔바른고딕, NanumBarunGothic, NanumBarunGothicOTF; font-size: 14pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&#34&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-all; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);&#34&gt;&lt;span lang=&#34en-us&#34 xml:lang=&#34en-us&#34 style=&#34box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13pt;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 나눔바른고딕, NanumBarunGothic, NanumBarunGothicOTF; font-size: 14pt;&#34&gt;&lt;br style=&#34box-sizing: border-box;&#34&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-all; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);&#34&gt;&lt;span lang=&#34en-us&#34 xml:lang=&#34en-us&#34 style=&#34box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 나눔고딕, NanumGothic; letter-spacing: 0pt; font-size: 13pt;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 나눔바른고딕, NanumBarunGothic, NanumBarunGothicOTF; font-size: 14pt;&#34&gt;&lt;br style=&#34box-sizing: border-box;&#34&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-all; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 나눔바른고딕, NanumBarunGothic, NanumBarunGothicOTF; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&#34&gt;&lt;b style=&#34box-sizing: border-box;&#34&gt;[담당 변호사]&nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34box-sizing: border-box; word-break: break-all; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102);&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14pt; font-family: 나눔바른고딕, NanumBarunGothic, NanumBarunGo