4 1.8;&#34=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34 style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; color: rgb(125, 125, 125);&#34&gt;&lt;span noto=&#34&#34 sans=&#34&#34 kr&#34,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;&#34=&#34&#34 style=&#34border: 0px; font-size: 24pt; vertical-align: top; position: relative; line-height: normal;&#34&gt;한국도선안전교육연구센터&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&#34center&#34 malgun=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 &#34맑은=&#34&#34 고딕&#34,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -1px;=&#34&#34 text-align:=&#34&#34 center;&#34=&#34&#34 nanum=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 -0.2px;=&#34&#34 border:=&#34&#34 0px;=&#34&#34 font-size:=&#34&#34 22px;=&#34&#34 vertical-align:=&#34&#34 top;=&#34&#34 position:=&#34&#34 relative;=&#34&#34 line-height:=&#34&#34 1.8;&#34=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34 style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; color: rgb(125, 125, 125);&#34&gt;&lt;span noto=&#34&#34 sans=&#34&#34 kr&#34,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;&#34=&#34&#34 style=&#34border: 0px; font-size: 24pt; vertical-align: top; position: relative; line-height: normal;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 이사장 조 용 화&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','','',262,'','','','','','20231205091233.pdf','23-12월 항내운항안전교육 실시계획.pdf','','','','','','','','','','',410,0,0,'104.28.212.167','2023-12-05 09:50:56','1',410,'',NULL,''),(411,'notice',0,'2024년도 1월 항내운항안전교육 실시 안내','','관리자','safsa@dsfasf','admin',0,'','','','','&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 22px;&#34&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-family: 궁서체;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2024년도 1월 항내운항안전교육 실시 안내&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; 우리 센터는 선박 조종 이론 습득 및 선교자원간 커뮤니케이션 역량 강화를 위해 아래와 같이&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;2024년도 1월 항내 운항 안전 교육&#34을 실시하오니 많은 참여 바랍니다.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;- 아&nbsp; 래 -&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&lt;b&gt;&nbsp; 가. 교육 개요&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;○ 일&nbsp; 시 : 2024. 1. 24.(수), 09:30 ~ 16:30&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;○ 장&nbsp; 소 : 부산, 한국선원센터 4층 중강의실&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;○ 대&nbsp; 상 : 선장 및 선장 진급 예정자&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp;○ 정&nbsp; 원 : 30명 내외 (선착순 마감)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;○ 교육비: 400,000원/1인 (교재 제공, 중식 미제공)&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&lt;b&gt;&nbsp; 나. 교육 신청 절차&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;○ 온라인 접수(교육일 기준 3주 전 ~ 2일 전까지 가능)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - 홈페이지 회원가입 후 교육 예약 &gt; 교육 신청&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;※ 신청자 10인 미만인 경우 교육과정 개설이 취소(연기)될 수 있습니다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;○ 교육비 납부 (40만원)&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - 계좌이체 : (우리은행) 1005-602-307716 (예금주) (사)한국도선안전교육연구센터&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - 교육시작 2일전까지 납부&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&nbsp;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 16px;&#34&gt; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;※ 교육시작 전 교육비 납입이 안될 경우 예약이 자동취소 됩니다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&lt;b&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;다. 교육 이수자에 대한 혜택&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&nbsp; &lt;span style=&#34font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;○ 도선료 한시적 할인&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&nbsp;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 16px;&#34&gt; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; -&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;도선료 할인 안내는 한국도선사협회 홈페이지(www.kmpilot.or.kr) 참고.&nbsp; 끝.&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;span style=&#34font-family: 궁서체;&#34&gt; &nbsp; 2024년 1월 4일&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 20px; font-family: 궁서체;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;한국도선안전교육연구센터&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &lt;span style=&#34font-size: 18px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 22px;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 18px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-family: 궁서체; font-size: 18px;&#34&gt;이사장 조 용 화&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span&gt;﻿&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;﻿&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;','','',319,'','','','','','20240119130120.pdf','2024년 1월 항내운항안전교육 실시계획.pdf','','','','','','','','','','',411,0,0,'104.28.223.14','2024-01-04 09:24:09','1',411,'',NULL,''),(412,'notice',0,'2024년도 2월 항내운항안전교육 실시 안내','','관리자','safsa@dsfasf','admin',0,'','','','','&lt;p style=&#34color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34 nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 22px;&#34&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-family: 궁서체;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-family: 맑은고딕;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 