10인 미만인 경우 교육과정 개설이 취소(연기)될 수 있습니다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34 nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;○ 교육비 납부 (40만원)&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34 nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - 계좌이체 : (우리은행) 1005-602-307716 (예금주) (사)한국도선안전교육연구센터&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34 nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - 교육시작 2일전까지 납부&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34 nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-s