ic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34 style=&#34color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;○ 온라인 접수(교육일 기준 3주 전 ~ 2일 전까지 가능)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34 style=&#34color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; - 홈페이지 회원 가입 후 교육 예약 &gt; 교육 신청&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34 style=&#34color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;※ 신청자 10인 미만인 경우 신청 마감 전이라도 교육 과정 개설이 취소(연기)될 수 있습니다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34 style=&#34color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px