thic&#34, 돋움, dotum, AppleGothic, &#34Apple SD Gothic Neo Medium&#34, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;     ○ 교육비: 500,000원/1인 (교재 제공, 중식비 지원)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34 style=&#34color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34Nanum Gothic&#34, NanumGothic, &#34Malgun Gothic&#34, 돋움, dotum, AppleGothic, &#34Apple SD Gothic Neo Medium&#34, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34 style=&#34color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34Nanum Gothic&#34, NanumGothic, &#34Malgun Gothic&#34, 돋움, dotum, AppleGothic, &#34Apple SD Gothic Neo Medium&#34, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&lt;b&gt;  나. 교육 신청 절차&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34 style=&#34color