color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34Nanum Gothic&#34, NanumGothic, &#34Malgun Gothic&#34, 돋움, dotum, AppleGothic, &#34Apple SD Gothic Neo Medium&#34, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;           ※ 신청자 10인 미만인 경우 신청 마감 전이라도 교육 과정 개설이 취소(연기)될 수 있습니다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34 style=&#34color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34Nanum Gothic&#34, NanumGothic, &#34Malgun Gothic&#34, 돋움, dotum, AppleGothic, &#34Apple SD Gothic Neo Medium&#34, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;           ※ 원활한 교육 실시를 위해 가급적 교육일 일주일 전에 신청을 완료 해주시기 바라며, 교육 1일 전에는 교육 신청이 불가합니다.   &lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34 helvetica,=&#34&#34 arial,=&#34&#34 sans-serif;=&#34&#34 letter-spacing:=&#34&#34 -0.2px;&#34=&#34&#34 style=&#34color: rgb(125, 125, 125); font-family: &#34Nanum Gothic&#34, NanumGothic, &#34Malgun Gothic&#34, 돋움, dotum, AppleGothic, &#34Apple SD Gothic Neo Medium&#34, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34letter-spacing: -0.2px; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;     ○ 교육비 납부 (50만원) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p nanum=&#34&#34 gothic&#34,=&#34&#34 nanumgothic,=&#34&#34 &#34malgun=&#34&#34 돋움,=&#34&#34 dotum,=&#34&#34 applegothic,=&#34&#34 &#34apple=&#34&#34 sd=&#34&#34 gothic=&#34&#34 neo=&#34&#34 medium&#34,=&#34&#34