i: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;해양수산부와 (사)한국도선안전교육연구센터는 항만 입출항 과정에서 발생하는 선박사고 예방을 위해 도선 시뮬레이터 등 도선사 교육실습 장비를 지원하는 사업을 2023년부터 2024년까지 30억원을 투입하여 추진하고 있다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;이번에 도입하는 도선 시뮬레이터는 실제 선박을 조정하는 선교 공간과 장비를 그대로 구현하고, 기상 악화, 선박 화재, 침수 발생 등 다양한 상황에서 훈련이 가능하여 도선사의 전문성 향상과 함께 재난안전 대응 능력을 키우는데 많은 도움이 될 것으로 기대된다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;한편 한국도선안전교육연구센터에서는 도선 시뮬레이터 설치 및 전문적인 교육 프로그램 제공을 위해 교육 공간을 새롭게 이전하게 됨에 따라 이를 기념하는 개소 행사도 같이 열린다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;개소 행사 이후에는 한국도선사협회에서 2022년도부터 자체적으로 추진하고 있는 도선사의 날 기념행사도 개최하여 도선 업무의 중요성을 널리 알리고 도선사의 노고를 격려하는 시간을 보낼 예정이다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;강도형 해양수산부 장관은 “수에즈 운하 좌초 사고 사례와 같이 최근 선박 대형화로 인해 해상사고 발생시 피해규모가 천문학적으로 확대될 수 있는 만큼, 이를 예방하는 정책이 매우 중요하다.”라며, “이번 도선시뮬레이터 도입을 통해 도선사의 전문성을 강화하여 항만 입출항 과정에서 발생하는 선박 사고를 대폭 감소할 수 있기를 바란다.“라고 밝혔다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;&#34&gt;&lt;strong style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-size: 24px;&#34&gt;Introduction of the Latest Pilotage Simulator to Prevent Maritime Accidents&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;&#34&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal; text-align: center;&#34&gt;&lt;strong style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3;&#34&gt;- Opening ceremony for the relocation and expansion of the Korea Pilot Education Center and the 3rd Pilot&#39s Day commemoration ceremony.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;&#34&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;&#34&gt;&nbsp;The Ministry of Oceans and Fisheries (MOF) has announced that it will introduce a state-of-the-art pilotage simulator to prevent maritime traffic accidents and enhance the capabilities of Korean pilots.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;&#34&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;&#34&gt;&nbsp;The MOF and Korea Pilot Education Center (KOPEC) are investing KRW 3 billion between 2023 and 2024 in a project to support pilotage training equipment, such as pilotage simulators, to prevent he kinds of ship accidents that occur while ships are entering and exiting ports.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;&#34&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;&#34&gt;&nbsp;The pilotage simulator being introduced on this occasion is expected to greatly improve pilots&#39 expertise and disaster safety response capabilities by replicating the actual ship steering space and equipment and allowing training in various situations, such as adverse weather conditions, ship fires, and flooding.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;&#34&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;&#34&gt;&nbsp;Meanwhile, KOPEC will hold an opening ceremony to commemorate the move to a new educational space in which it will install the pilot simulator and provide a specialized educational curriculum.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;&#34&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;Pretendard GOV&quot;, sans-serif; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: normal; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-variant-alternates: inherit; font-variant-position: inherit; font-variant-emoji: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 18px; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34text-size-adjust: none; max-height: 1e+06px; font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;; scroll-behavior: smooth; line-height: inherit; letter-spacing: inherit; font-size: inherit; word-break: keep-all; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-optical-sizing: inherit; font-size-adjust: inherit; font-kerning: inherit; font-feature-settings: inherit; font-variation-settings: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;&#34&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&#34text-size-adjust: 100%; max-height: 1e+06px; line-height: 1.3; word-break: keep-all; font-family: Roboto, Pretendard, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; letter-spacing: normal;&#34&gt;&nbsp;After the opening ceremony, the Korea Maritime Pilots Association will also hold a “Pilots Day” commemoration event, which it has promoted since 2022, to raise awareness of the importance of pilots&#39 work and to encourage them to work harder.&lt;/p&gt;','','',27,'','','','','','20250821110809.jpg','AUG00076.jpg','20250821110809.pdf','240902(조간) 해상사고 예방을 위한 최신 도선 시뮬레이터 도입(항만물류산업과).pdf','','','','','','','','',471,0,0,'112.218.177.231','2024-09-02 00:00:00','1',471,'','',''),(472,'notice',0,'2025년도 9월 항내운항안전교육 심화 과정 실시 안내','','관리자','','admin',0,'','','','','&lt;div style=&#34color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; border: 0px; word-break: break-all; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.04em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34border: 0px; font-size: 24px; font-family: 맑은고딕; color: inherit; word-break: break-all; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.2px;&#34&gt;&lt;b style=&#34border: 0px; font-size: inherit; font-family: inherit; color: inherit; word-break: break-all; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.04em;&#34&gt;﻿2025년 9월 항내운항안전교육 심화 과정 실시 안내&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#34color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; border: 0px; word-break: break-all; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.04em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: inherit; color: inherit; word-break: break-all; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.04em;&#34&gt;&lt;br style=&#34word-break: break-all;&#34&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#34color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; border: 0px; word-break: break-all; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.04em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: inherit; color: inherit; word-break: break-all; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.04em;&#34&gt;우리 센터는 선박 조종 이론 습득 및 선교 자원 간 커뮤니케이션 역량 강화를 위해 아래와 같이 2025년도 9월 항내운항안전교육(심화 과정)을 실시하오니 많은 참여 바랍니다.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&#34color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; border: 0px; word-break: break-all; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: -0.04em; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5;&#34&gt;&lt;span style=&#34border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: inherit; color: inherit; word-break: bre